#

Pumpkin Pasta Alla Vodka

30 min
$12.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyPastaComfort Food

Description

Creamy and comforting pasta with a hint of pumpkin and a splash of vodka, perfect for a cozy dinner.

Ingredients

  • pasta (penne or fusilli): 8 oz
  • pumpkin puree: 1 cup
  • vodka: 1/2 cup
  • heavy cream: 1/2 cup
  • parmesan cheese (grated): 1/2 cup
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • red pepper flakes: optional, to taste
